     426/    E9C1 : 2B 11                               BMI     INCTRK                   ;
     427/    E9C3 : F6 EC 01                            LDAB    PIAREGB                  ; 
     428/    E9C6 : C4 BF                               ANDB    #$BF                     ; Reset Side (= Side 1)
     429/    E9C8 : F7 EC 01                            STAB    PIAREGB                  ; 
     430/    E9CB : 80 1A                               SUBA    #26                      ; We have Sector 27 - 27 = 0 - 26 carry is set, for 53-27=26-26 carry is clear
